text: Katie Findlay (born August 28, 1990) is a Canadian actress. She is best known for her role as Rosie Larsen in the American crime drama television series The Killing. From 2014 to 2015, Findlay played Rebecca Sutter in the first season of the ABC series How to Get Away with Murder. Findlay was born in Windsor, Ontario.
